        "text": "Multi-Site Construction & Program Management Company\n\nOver $1 billion in multi-site remodels and renovations, touching 14,000 stores annually.\n\nJoin our team — experience a company culture that values you.\n\nSevan Multi-Site Solutions is a construction project management company trusted by many of the world’s top brands when they need to expand or refresh multiple locations at once. From remodels to rebrands to new expansions, we provide complete construction management from start to finish. Whether we’re called upon to handle an entire program or just a portion of it, our project management professionals act as an extension of your team. Our integrated construction site management solutions minimize disruptions, eliminate waste, and prevent confusion that can drag down your project and lead to costly delays.\n\nWhat we do\n\nWe partner with you to modernize and grow within your industry by helping you control change across your end-to-end suite of solutions.\n\nLearn more\n\nHow we do it\n\nOur customized solutions and onsite teams give you the reassurance and confidence to complete your project through a smooth, expedited process.\n\nLearn more\n\nWho we are\n\nWe are proud to be leaders in the industry and, most importantly, your collaborative partner every step of the way, from start to finish.\n\nLearn more\n\nLearn more\n\n“\n\nWe chose Seven because of your reputation. McDonald’s has a long history with Sevan and they’ve been a valuable part of our team.”\n\nSevan is fast to invest in and bring on the talent needed to get any project headed in the right direction.”\n\nSevan’s quick-service restaurant knowledge is strong. Your day-to-day activities of completing projects brings expertise to our team.”\n\nSevan is multi-faceted and has a lot to offer. It’s exciting to work with a company whose team is so positive and engaging.”\n\nSevan is on the front foot of innovation, always looking to what we can do better.”\n\nSevan talks with you, considers you, and engages with you—executing on their message of safety and excellence by bringing people who care about what they do.”\n\nSevan has an impressive footprint and scale across the company. They have culture, capacity and bring energy to the conversation.”\n\nSevan’s technology side of the business is a differentiator, offering a systematic approach to developing projects and tracking them.”\n\nSevan brings real expertise that you can’t find anywhere. They deliver above and beyond what they are asked to do in a professional, courteous manner.”\n\nPrevious\n\nNext\n\nOur experience\n\nSpeed to market starts with The Strength of Sevan\n\nUnderstanding of restaurant customer flow, kitchen equipment requirements and DT layouts.\n\nKnowledge of multiple retail survey operations, including grocery, apparel, C-store, pharmacy and general merchandise.\n\nExpertise in asset conditions, capital planning and safety and stability of structures.\n\nrestaurant refreshes\n\n0\n\nretail refreshes\n\n0\n\nhealthcare refreshes\n\n0\n\nsq. ft. surveyed\n\n0 B\n\nYou only have two hands.\n\nThink what you could do with Sevan.\n\nContact us\n\nWhy you should choose us\n\nAs your full-service source for construction contract management across your entire operations, we offer an integrated, streamlined approach. We can be your program management company for only a portion of the work or the entire project lifecycle. No matter what you choose, you can count on us to provide customized solutions instead of an out-of-the-box plan. To learn more about how our project management company can become an extension of your team, get in touch with us today.\n\nJoin our team\n\nExperience a company culture that values you.\n\nSevan is an outstanding, best-in-class place to work. And it’s not just us saying that:\n\nIn partnership with the global analytics firm Great Place to Work®, Fortune named Sevan one of 2023’s Best Workplaces in Chicago\n\nWe’ve been recognized as a Great Place to Work ten years in a row, and a top 25 Best Place to Work in Illinois five years straight\n\nThese prestigious honors are all based on what Sevan team members have said about their experience working with us\n\nThanks to the talent and hard work of all our team members, we continue to grow and are looking to hire more inspired, entrepreneurial people\n\nWhy work at Sevan?"
